e topic, the post gets wiped.      <BR>      <BR> 3) Posts specificially trolling for flames as the main topic of discussion get the thread wiped because whatever opinion or truth may be, it doesn't have much to do with EQ or druids.     <BR>  <BR> 4) Whether they are true or not, posts whose primary purpose is to rant about individual in-game players or guilds as being killstealers, exploiters, or other accusations will be moved to the rants section. <BR>  <BR> 5) The use of Java scripts or other runtime-languages are NOT ALLOWED. If you have any scripted content in your post, and it is found, you will have the entire post removed, regradless of what the topic of your post was. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uelial.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Elial</A> at: 11/3/00 7:08:44 am<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroveboardpostingrulesandpolicy.showMessage?topicID=3.topic"> << Prev Topic </a> &nbsp;| <br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroveboardpostingrulesandpolicy.emailToFriend?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend">Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroveboardpostingrulesandpolicy.threadControl?topicID=1.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroveboardpostingrulesandpolicy.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgroveboardpostingrulesandpolicy.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br